All done. Here's what was implemented:

**Code changes (wiring):**
- `app/index.tsx` — "Start Growing" now opens `NewGameModal` instead of navigating directly. Config (seed, mode, difficulty) flows into `resetGame()` before pushing to `/game`.
- `app/game/index.tsx` — `<TutorialOverlay targetRect={null} />` added. Reads `tutorialState` from store; shows the step label + Skip Tutorial button for the active tutorial.

**4 Maestro flows:**

| File | What it tests |
|------|--------------|
| `.maestro/new-game.yml` | Main menu → NewGameModal → Exploration mode → Begin Your Grove → game screen |
| `.maestro/tutorial.yml` | Game start → assert "Look around" step label → Skip Tutorial → assert dismissed |
| `.maestro/plant-tree.yml` | Game start → skip tutorial → joystick swipe → assert + tap PLANT action button |
| `.maestro/pause-menu.yml` | Game screen → Open menu → settings tab → Sound Effects visible → Continue Playing → assert dismissed |

All selectors use `accessibilityLabel` (stable) or known text content. Touch targets are ≥44px as enforced by `minHeight` in each component's styles. `tsc` → 0 errors, `jest` → 3415/3415 pass.

